《'''中国公主'''》（''Princess Of China''）是[[Coldplay|Coldplay]]和[[Rihanna|Rihanna]]合作的歌曲，收录于Coldplay的第十五张专辑《[[Mylo_Xyloto|Mylo Xyloto]]》中，是第四支单曲。歌曲由Guy Berryman、Jonny Buckland、Will Champion、Chris Martin和Brian Eno辑写<ref>[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mylo_Xyloto Mylo Xyloto] {{Wayback|url=http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mylo_Xyloto |date=20201111234014 }} (inlay cover). Coldplay. EMI Records. 2011.</ref>，并在Rock、流行音乐、R&B音乐界产生了一定的影响力。歌曲于2012年二月14日在美国的电台播放，并于四月13日提供下载<ref>"[http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/princess-of-china/id471339278?i=471339674 Mylo Xylto] {{Wayback|url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/princess-of-china/id471339278?i=471339674 |date=20111118100455 }}". iTunes Store. Apple. 2011-10-25. Retrieved 2011-10-25.</ref>。

==排行情况==
歌曲在网络上备受好评，一段时间在[[Billboard_Hot_100|Billboard Hot 100]]（告示牌百强单曲榜）排行20<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2011-11-12/hot-100?order=gainer|title=Hot 100 – Biggest Jump|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|accessdate= 2012-08-08}}</ref>，在[[英国单曲排行榜|英国单曲排行榜]]一度排行第33<ref name="uk">{{cite web|url=http://www.theofficialcharts.com/search-results-album/_/Princess+Of+China+ft+Rihanna#single|title=The Official Charts Company - Princess Of China ft Rihanna by Coldplay Search|date=2013-05-06|publisher=The Official Charts Company}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> ，并进入年度最畅销的单曲列表<ref name="chartuk">{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-singles-of-2012-revealed-1784/ |title=The Official Top 40 Biggest Selling Singles Of 2012 revealed! |author=Dan Lane |publisher=Official Charts Company |date=2013-01-02 |accessdate=2013-01-05 |archive-date=2014-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007161714/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/the-official-top-40-biggest-selling-singles-of-2012-revealed-1784/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 。"Princess of China" 2011年11月12日在[[Canadian_Hot_100|加拿大排行榜]]排到第十七，则达到了其数字下载的最狂热时期<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/2011-11-12/canadian-hot-100?order=gainer|title=Canadian Hot 100 – Biggest Jump|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|accessdate=2012-08-08}}</ref>。

在丹麦， 歌曲于2011年11月4日排行第17，曾在排行榜上停留了十周。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.danishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Coldplay+%26+Rihanna&titel=Princess+Of+China&cat=s |title=Danishcharts.com – Coldplay & Rihanna – Princess Of China" . Tracklisten . |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2017-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806101234/http://danishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Coldplay+%26+Rihanna&titel=Princess+Of+China&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref> 歌曲在[[Finnish_Singles_Chart|芬兰单曲榜]]上则两周排名第14。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Coldplay+%26+Rihanna&titel=Princess+Of+China&cat=s |title="Coldplay & Rihanna: Princess of China" . Finnish Singles Chart . |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2016-03-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325185806/http://finnishcharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Coldplay+%26+Rihanna&titel=Princess+Of+China&cat=s |dead-url=no }}</ref>在德国则于2012年5月排行第97<ref>[http://www.charts.de/song.asp?artist=Coldplay+feat.+Rihanna&title=Princess+Of+China&cat=s&country=de  "Single – Coldplay feat. Rihanna, Princess Of China" (in German). Media Control Charts. Retrieved 2012-05-09.]{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

歌曲的MV由Adria Petty和Alan Bibby导演，于2012年三月在洛杉矶拍摄<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://twitter.com/#!/TaikoCenterLA/status/182733227126030337 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2018-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180728041220/https://twitter.com/#!/TaikoCenterLA/status/182733227126030337 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，并于2012年六月二日在网络上公布。MV包含了一个关于Rihanna和Chris Martin的爱情故事<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/coldplay-explores-martial-arts-in-princess-of-china-20120604 |title="Coldplay Explore Martial Arts in 'Princess of China'" . Rolling Stone. |accessdate=2013-07-30 |archive-date=2017-04-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170425133011/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/coldplay-explores-martial-arts-in-princess-of-china-20120604 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

